в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ parameter across all four center-to-edge connections. This reduces the per-block          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ parameter count (from 13 keys to 10 keys), lowering total parameters from 78 to 60 given  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ the same N_UPLOADS and N_REPEATS, while preserving the symmetry and data-uploading        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ structure. The change aims to improve training efficiency and generalization without      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ altering inputs/outputs or the fixed data/feature-map/training loop. All gates remain on  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ allowed adjacent grid edges, and the overall ansatz topology (pre-RZ, RY, CZ ring, hub    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ entanglement, post-RZ) is preserved.                                                      в”Ӯ
