в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ 1. First program (CRX hub): 78 params, score 0.55, test_acc 0.47                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ 2. Second program (CRZ hub, shared params): 60 params, score 0.57, test_acc 0.48          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ 3. Current program (CRZ hub, distinct params): 78 params, score 0.55, test_acc 0.52       в”Ӯ
