в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ Key observations:                                                                         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - The second program achieved the best score (0.57) with fewer parameters (60 vs 78)      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - It used parameter sharing on the hub entanglement (all 4 edges shared one               в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ "crz_hub_edge" param)                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - Current program regressed to 78 params with distinct per-edge params, reducing          в”Ӯ
