в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ 2. Add diagonal entanglement between corners to capture board diagonal structure          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ 3. Add RX gates (in addition to RY) for richer single-qubit expressivity                  в”Ӯ
