в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - Reduces parameters for better efficiency (60 total)                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - Adds diagonal corner-to-corner CZ gates to capture win-line symmetries                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - Increases expressivity with RX rotations on corners                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - Maintains the validated hub-and-ring structure                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - Should improve validation accuracy back toward 0.60 while keeping test accuracy high    в”Ӯ
