в”Ӯ patch_type               в”Ӯ full                                                                                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ patch_name               в”Ӯ none                                                                                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ patch_description        в”Ӯ We propose a fundamentally different ansatz strategy that preserves the overall           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ data-reuploading, 9-qubit Tic-Tac-Toe encoding, and fixed training loop, but changes the  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ internal circuit design to be more expressive without increasing parameter count per      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ block. Key changes:                                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - Layered, symmetry-aware pre/post rotations: group-based sharing remains (corners,       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ edges, center) for both RZ and RY, but the coupling remains structured to leverage board  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ symmetry.                                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - Ring CZ along the outer edge remains to entangle perimeter qubits.                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - Hub entanglement switched to per-edge CRX between center and each edge (center-edge hub в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ CRX), enabling a more expressive, parameter-efficient center-to-edge interaction.         в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - Added a lightweight inter-edge entanglement stage using fixed CNOT gates along the      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ outer ring (0-1, 2-3, 4-5, 6-7) to promote information flow across the ring without       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ adding trainable parameters for these gates.                                              в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ - Post-rotation layer preserved with group sharing to keep parameter count per block at   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ 13, keeping total parameters at 78 (N_PARAMS = 13 * N_UPLOADS * N_REPEATS).               в”Ӯ
