в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ data-reuploading (l=3), 2-repeat per upload structure. Parameter sharing remains at the   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ group level for pre/post-RZ and RY layers, maintaining symmetry advantages and parameter  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ efficiency. This is intended to improve validation accuracy and reduce train-test gaps    в”Ӯ
