в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ symmetries while the ring/hub interactions provide richer inter-qubit correlations        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ without exploding the parameter budget. This mirrors the second programвҖҷs improvements    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ (0.60 combined score) by collapsing ring and hub gates to single shared parameters,       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                          в”Ӯ potentially improving generalization and convergence with Adam.                           в”Ӯ
